{"tid":1594484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"外交部：《願榮光歸香港》為港獨歌曲","createTime":"2019-09-25T14:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T00:44:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":201,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"b504f696e363c19426261cc3e3e4c967341bdef5","tid":1594484,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"香港反送中運動持續，預計 9.28 和 10.1 都有機會再次爆發大規模衝突；外交部駐港特派員公署副特派員宋如安，就向在港外國傳媒放話，指香港示威者揮舞英國、美國國旗，又破壞立法會和中聯辦，貶損國旗和國徽，還唱歌尋求獨立，有「光復香港、時代革命」等口號，是公然挑戰一國兩制紅線，顯露顏色革命和本土恐怖主義的特徵。<br />\n<br />\n宋如安在中環宴請外國傳媒時發言，指持續百多日的示威，除了要求特首林鄭月娥下台，又破壞立法會和中聯辦等，貶損國旗和國徽，煽動學生組人鏈，反修例歌曲是尋求「香港獨立」，口號亦包括「光復香港、時代革命」，「暴徒」的行為令人震驚不可接受，公然挑戰一國兩制紅線。"},{"pid":"d37c2490f82d9a9d89c0127dbccddcbbac1f82e4","tid":1594484,"uid":168522,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"自我實現的預言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8dab8f1238d218176ee619c47c5a3846f06d0b","tid":1594484,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37c2490f82d9a9d89c0127dbccddcbbac1f82e4","tid":1594484,"uid":168522,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"自我實現的預言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0bc1d7af82c5c3c90e85f31e3986195031e081","tid":1594484,"uid":183758,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"FUCK YOU CCP ALL GO TO HELL!"},{"pid":"cf503d2aa8edba78962ffefeafbd760fa12beef9","tid":1594484,"uid":251292,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"381aba1317abe9f204fa6f5f81cf0912b202817b","tid":1594484,"uid":182007,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"香港建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm